<h1 class="title" style="position: relative; top:25px; height:35px; width: 250px; margin-left: 785px;"> Welcome Back </h1><br>
<h3 class="title" style="position: relative; top:25px; height:35px; width: 800px; margin-left: 510px; margin-bottom:-15px"> Regime: </h3>
<h4 class="subtitle" style="position: relative; top:25px; height:15px; width: 1300px; margin-left: 250px;"> {{caloryMessage}} </h4><br>
<h4 class="subtitle" style="position: relative; top:25px; height:15px; width: 1300px; margin-left: 250px;"> {{BMIMessage}} </h4><br>
